<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_56d4d0043578.aspx"><b>甫田</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson56d4d0043578">
无田甫田，维莠骄骄。无思远人，劳心忉忉。<br />无田甫田，维莠桀桀。无思远人，劳心怛怛。<br />婉兮娈兮。总角丱兮。未几见兮，突而弁兮！
</div>
